{"tid":2001180,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"侯利亞：係時候頒冠軍畀利物浦","createTime":"2020-05-04T10:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T22:12:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fb78f3094ae7e336acd2255cef001f59b36dc902","tid":2001180,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:58:58.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】利物浦前領隊侯利亞認為，即使賽季不能恢復，也應該把冠軍頒予利物浦。<br />\n<br />\n1998&ndash;2004年執教利物浦6年，包括在2001年贏得歐協盃（歐霸盃前身）、英足盃及英聯盃成盃賽「3冠王」，偏偏未能領軍贏得英超冠軍的侯利亞（Gerard Houllier），深信在尚餘9輪比賽而在聯賽榜首放領25分的利物浦值得封王，贏得球會30年來首個頂級聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n侯利亞認為即使新型冠狀病毒最終導致英超未能復賽，也應該把冠軍頒予紅軍：「是的，那是法國的處理方法，（冠軍）給予巴黎聖日耳門，他們領先12分，而我認為利物浦只需要兩場比賽就贏冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n這名72歲法國籍名帥續說：「如果分差也許只是2、3分，那麼你還可以為給予落後球隊一些機會而爭辯，但25分不可能不成為冠軍，他們配得上。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"f527f38daab8712d9019d25e36124a69ae0e5fe9","tid":2001180,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://theunionjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/maxreeeesdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheunionjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fmaxreeeesdefault.jpg&h=d7232e88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05b7d03bf2fb3ff1709d5fe11e43cfcf5b1c5383","tid":2001180,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"比個冠軍利有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最煩係升降班果幾隊難settel"},{"pid":"5bc645ebfd3fac74adf20a17ba23ab06d028fea7","tid":2001180,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b7d03bf2fb3ff1709d5fe11e43cfcf5b1c5383","tid":2001180,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"比個冠軍利有咩所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最煩係升降班果幾隊難settel"},"citedBy":0